&lt;p>You cannot draw a straight line.&lt;br>
You cannot draw two parallel lines.&lt;br>
But you can see a section of line straight on a piece of paper.&lt;br>
You can see two sections of lines parallel on a paper.&lt;br>
If you extend the line beyond the page in the space&lt;br>
you will be surprised to know it is forming a circle.&lt;br>
Unfortunately, we don&amp;rsquo;t have that much life or&lt;br>
that long paper to draw on the canvas and we conclude the line is straight.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Diwali 2021</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/wiaposts/diwali-2021/</link><pubDate>Tue, 02 Nov 2021 08:33:00 +0530</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/wiaposts/diwali-2021/</guid><description>&lt;p>
