&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>A yearly festival of Deepavali has come&lt;br>
People are wishing each other,&lt;br>
Doing the shopping, giving gifts, and receiving gifts.&lt;br>
People are lighting lamps so that&lt;br>
the darkness around can be removed.&lt;br>
This lamp will light for a few hours and days&lt;br>
and remove the darkness around.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Happy Deepawali 2019</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/wiaposts/happy-deepawali-2019/</link><pubDate>Sun, 17 Jun 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/wiaposts/happy-deepawali-2019/</guid><description>&lt;p>
